  "text": "It has been demonstrated that the mitochondrial DnA content changes differently in various tissues during aging, probably reflecting functional diversities [CITATION_1] . We recently described reduced mitochondrial membrane potential and increased proton leak in aging tissues [CITATION_2] . However, we did not address either the origin of such modifications or the difference among tissues.",
